  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/bf90b738dee93cbd45952a1094cb47f9.avif?t=1772418612\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remy, a demon lord who neglected her duties and led a life of laziness, faced betrayal from her subordinates. Unable to tolerate her idle behavior any longer, they cast a \"Weakening Curse\" on her and threw her out of the Demon Castle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To lift the \"Weakening Curse,\" Remy needs to collect four \"Stones of Dispel,\" each held by one of her subordinates. Determined to break the curse and reclaim the Demon Castle, she embarks on a challenging quest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Remy manage to lift the curse and return to her leisurely life once more? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/921dd3392b59aeca3e3eb6fbd8dc71b4.avif?t=1772418612\" width=780 height=78 /></span>This game is an action RPG. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players control Remy, utilizing various skills to fight through monsters and conquer the dungeon-like Demon Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/1b9b4f04454c73e12aafcb8a562baf05.avif?t=1772418612\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide array of skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully customizable controls</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/bf90b738dee93cbd45952a1094cb47f9.avif?t=1772418612\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remy, a demon lord who neglected her duties and led a life of laziness, faced betrayal from her subordinates. Unable to tolerate her idle behavior any longer, they cast a \"Weakening Curse\" on her and threw her out of the Demon Castle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To lift the \"Weakening Curse,\" Remy needs to collect four \"Stones of Dispel,\" each held by one of her subordinates. Determined to break the curse and reclaim the Demon Castle, she embarks on a challenging quest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Remy manage to lift the curse and return to her leisurely life once more? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/921dd3392b59aeca3e3eb6fbd8dc71b4.avif?t=1772418612\" width=780 height=78 /></span>This game is an action RPG. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players control Remy, utilizing various skills to fight through monsters and conquer the dungeon-like Demon Castle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028010/extras/1b9b4f04454c73e12aafcb8a562baf05.avif?t=1772418612\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide array of skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully customizable controls</p></li></ul>",
